     H            Y
     F** ALCRS5 *******************************************************
     F*  GET SORT/SHIPPING SCAN DATE/TIME                             *
     F*  (COPIED FROM AJSR1Z)                                         *
     F*  J.WATANABE  2018.02.22                                       *
JW1  F*  J.WATANABE  2018.10.18 CHG SORT SCAN DATE/TIME               *
JW2  F*  J.WATANABE  2018.12.13 ADD SHIPPING AS A 2ND BARCODE         *
     F*  LEC         2024.01.11 ADD SHIPPING PRIORITY BARCODE         *
     F*---------------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'ALCRS5'
     F*                    PARM           $SHN1   5
     F*                    PARM           $SHN2   5
     F*                    PARM           $SHN3   2
     F*                    PARM           $ORD    3
     F*                    PARM           $IDAT   8
     F*                    PARM           $SDAT   8
     F*                    PARM           $STIM   6
     F*                    PARM           $STK    1
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*  IN  $SHN1 :  5A IAF PART1
     F*      $SHN2 :  5A IAF PART2
     F*      $SHN3 :  2A IAF PART3
     F*      $ORD  :  3A ORD# (TEHI)
     F*      $IDAT :  8A ISSUE DATE
     F*  OUT $SDAT :  8A SCAN DATE
     F*      $STIM :  6A SCAN TIME
     F*      $STK  :  1A STOCK Y/N
     F*      $RTN  :  1A RETURN CODE (BLANK/*)
     F*****************************************************************
      *  SORTING SCAN RESULTS FILE
     FALCPL07 IF  E           K        DISK
     FNZUPL02 IF  E           K        DISK
      *===============================================================
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W$PGM
     I                                      244 253 W$WSID
     I                                      254 263 W$USER
     I                                      264 269 W$JBNO
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140@TIME
     I                                        1   60@SYSTM
     I                                        7  140@SYSHZ
      *===============================================================
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C* IN ------
     C                     PARM           P@SHN1  5        PART 1
     C                     PARM           P@SHN2  5        PART 2
     C                     PARM           P@SHN3  2        PART 3
     C                     PARM           P@TEHI  3        PRODUCT ORDER
     C                     PARM           P@IDAT  8        ISSUE DATE
     C* OUT ------
     C                     PARM           P@SDAT  8        SCAN DATE
     C                     PARM           P@STIM  6        SCAN TIME
     C                     PARM           P@STK   1        STOCK Y/N
     C                     PARM           P@RTN   1        RETURN
      *------------------------*
     C           K@ALC     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           P@SHN1
     C                     KFLD           P@SHN2
     C                     KFLD           P@SHN3
     C                     KFLD           P@TEHI
     C           K@NZU     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           P@SHN1
     C                     KFLD           P@SHN2
     C                     KFLD           P@SHN3
     C                     KFLD           N@IDAT
      *===============================================================
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    P@SDAT
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    P@STIM
     C                     MOVE 'N'       P@STK
     C                     MOVE '*'       P@RTN
JW1  C                     MOVELP@IDAT    N@IDAT  80
      * GET SCAN DATE/TIME
     C           K@ALC     SETLLALCPL07
      *
     C           *IN90     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           K@ALC     READEALCPL07                  90
      *
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *OFF
JW1  C           A8DATE    ANDGEN@IDAT
      *
     C                     MOVELA8BRC2    LTR3    3
     C                     MOVELA8BRC2    LTR8    8
JW2  C           LTR3      IFEQ 'SRT'
"    C           LTR8      OREQ 'SHIPPING'
     C           LTR8      OREQ 'SH PRIOR'
     C                     MOVELA8DATE    P@SDAT
     C                     MOVELA8TIME    P@STIM
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    P@RTN
      ***************      LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      * shipping priority parts will be displayed in pink...
     C           LTR8      IFEQ 'SH PRIOR'
     C                     MOVE 'P'       P@STK
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * GET STOCK INFO
     C**JW1                MOVELP@IDAT    N@IDAT  80
     C           K@NZU     SETLLNZUPL02
      *
     C           *IN91     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           K@NZU     READENZUPL02                  91
     C           *IN91     IFEQ *OFF
     C           N2TEHI    ANDEQP@TEHI
     C           N2NYHZ    IFNE 0
     C           N2DEHZ    ORNE 0
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       P@STK
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *===============================================================
